<h1 id="hd_id421654218230011">Minimal Row Height</h1>
<section id="minimal_row_height_text">
<switch select="appl">
<case select="WRITER">
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id581605991965966">Adjust the height of the selected cells to the height of the content in the selected cells.</paragraph>
</case>
<case select="CALC"><comment>Not in CALC</comment>
</case>
<default>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id801654217365035">Adjust the height of the selected rows to the height of the selected content.</paragraph>
</default>
</switch>
</section>
  <section id="howtoget">
  <embed href="shared/00/00040500.xhp#minimal_row_height"/>
  </section>
<switch select="appl">
<case select="WRITER">
</case>
<case select="CALC"><comment>Not in CALC - MAYBE SWITCH NOT NEEDED HERE?</comment>
</case>
<default>
</default>
</switch>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id971654479023479">To minimize a single row, it is sufficient to place the cursor in a cell in the row.</paragraph>
  <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id1001653629678905">To minimize multiple rows, it is sufficient to select one cell from each row to be minimized.</paragraph>

